4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper's theoretical analysis and use of algorithms for personal recommendation may fall under the umbrella of machine learning. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper's focus on the relationship between different recommendation methods may involve the use of data structures and algorithms.
